<title>CodexSkillManager-1.3.0</title>
<body>
<h2>CodexSkillManager-1.3.0</h2>
<p>What’s New in Codex Skill Manager 1.3.0</p>
<ul>
<li>Add support for custom project skill folders alongside your user directory.</li>
<li>Fix deleting skills so it only removes entries from the selected folder.</li>
<li>Fix opening skill folders for custom path installs when the same slug exists elsewhere.</li>
<li>Make Markdown content selectable for easier copying.</li>
<li>Add GitHub Copilot as a supported platform.</li>
<li>Refresh the app icon and add a new About window.</li>
</ul>
</body>
</html>]]></description>
